                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item" style="--position: 4">
                        <div class="cert-card">
                            <img src="/certs/cert4.png" alt="Certification 4" class="cert-img" />
                            <h3>Cybersecurity Compliance</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item" style="--position: 5">
                        <div class="cert-card">
                            <img src="/certs/cert5.png" alt="Certification 5" class="cert-img" />
                            <h3>Defense Standards</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        <section class="news-section">
            <h1 class="section-title">Latest News & Updates</h1>
            <div class="news-grid">
                <article class="news-card">
                    <div class="news-header press-release">Press Release</div>
                    <div class="news-image agl-demo"></div>
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3 class="news-title">Vardhman AGL Systems Successfully Demonstrates Advanced LED
                            Technology</h3>
                        <p class="news-excerpt">Vardhman announced the successful performance of advanced LED inset
                            lighting systems at major Indian airports. The implementation showcases cutting-edge
                            technology in airfield ground lighting solutions.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more-btn">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="news-card">
                    <div class="news-header in-news">In The News</div>
                    <div class="news-image rocket-launch"></div>
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3 class="news-title">Vardhman's Advanced AVDGS Systems Achieve 100% Performance Standards
                        </h3>
                        <p class="news-excerpt">Vardhman Airport Solutions has announced that its Advanced Visual
                            Docking Guidance Systems (AVDGS) have successfully completed performance testing,
                            meeting international aviation standards for precision aircraft guidance.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more-btn">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="news-card">
                    <div class="news-header press-release">Press Release</div>
                    <div class="news-image contract-award"></div>
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3 class="news-title">Vardhman Receives ₹45 Crore AGL Infrastructure Contract Award</h3>
                        <p class="news-excerpt">Vardhman, the leader in airport lighting solutions, has been
                            selected as the prime contractor for a major AGL infrastructure project. The contract
                            includes design, supply, installation and commissioning of complete lighting systems.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#" class="read-more-btn">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

